\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 28.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 This is clearly not an exhaustive list of factors but any additional factors taken into account by the Commission must be relevant to competition. These factors are typical of those that an agency engaged in merger analysis would have regard to and in acco
