\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f2\fs22\f3\fs22\f2\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 36.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af2\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang1033\loch\f2\fs22\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0 It is the Commission, as the investigator, who gathers information, conducts interviews, conducts visits to the operations of merging parties and competitors alike, peruses internal strategic documents, gathers econometric evidence and through this process
