\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 66.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 As far as the filing of the supplementary affidavit is concerned, the applicant submits that they required Mr Crickmay\'92s input and had to wait until he had looked through the record of proceedings.  The status of the supplementary affidavit remains uncerta
