\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 69.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 Having regard to all the factors above, we accordingly find that the applicant\'92s delay of some 75 business days in bringing the review application was unreasonable in the circumstances of this case, and does not warrant this Tribunal overlooking it.  Indee
